{"word":"G4724 - στέλλω - stéllō - stel'-lo - Avoid","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">στέλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">stéllō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">stel'-lo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Avoid</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விலகு"},{"paragraph":"1. to set, place, set in order, arrange; to fit out, to prepare, equip"},{"paragraph":"2. to bring together, contract, shorten"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably strengthened from the base of <a href=\"#/G2476 - ἵστημι - hístēmi - his'-tay-mee/2476\">G2476</a>; properly to <i>set</i> fast (&ldquo;stall&rdquo;), that is, (figuratively) to <i>repress</i> (reflexively <i>abstain</i> from associating with): - avoid, withdraw self.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1291/1291\">G1291</a>, <a href=\"#/G1293/1293\">G1293</a>, <a href=\"#/G1989/1989\">G1989</a>, <a href=\"#/G1992/1992\">G1992</a>, <a href=\"#/G2687/2687\">G2687</a>, <a href=\"#/G2689/2689\">G2689</a>, <a href=\"#/G4724/4724\">G4724</a>, <a href=\"#/G4958/4958\">G4958</a>, <a href=\"#/G5288/5288\">G5288</a>, <a href=\"#/G5289/5289\">G5289</a>"}]}